## SS 4. Like Post

Navigate to post, wait 2s.

Like buttons: `aria-label="Like (N)"` on posts, text "Like" on notes. "Unlike" = already liked.

```bash
exec curl -s -X POST http://localhost:3847/api/browser/{{browser_profile}}/evaluate -H 'Content-Type: application/json' -d @- <<'ENDJSON'
{"fn":"async () => { await new Promise(r => setTimeout(r, 2000)); var btns = Array.from(document.querySelectorAll('button')); var likeBtn = btns.find(b => { var label = (b.getAttribute('aria-label') || '').toLowerCase(); return label.startsWith('like'); }); if (!likeBtn) { likeBtn = btns.find(b => b.innerText.trim() === 'Like'); } if (!likeBtn) return { error: 'like button not found' }; var label = (likeBtn.getAttribute('aria-label') || '').toLowerCase(); if (label.startsWith('unlike')) return { alreadyLiked: true }; likeBtn.dispatchEvent(new MouseEvent('click', { bubbles: true, cancelable: true })); await new Promise(r => setTimeout(r, 1000)); var newLabel = likeBtn.getAttribute('aria-label') || ''; return { liked: true, newLabel: newLabel }; }"}
ENDJSON
```

